    @Generated(value={"RichFaces CDK","4.5.0-SNAPSHOT"})
public class HtmlInputNumberSpinner
extends AbstractInputNumberSpinner
implements javax.faces.component.behavior.ClientBehaviorHolder, AccesskeyProps, CoreProps, EventsKeyProps, EventsMouseProps, FocusProps, I18nProps, InputProps

    The &lt;r:inputNumberSpinner&gt; component is a single-line input field with buttons to increase and decrease a numerical value. The value can be changed using the corresponding directional keys on a keyboard, or by typing into the field.
